{"tid":528639,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"和式踎廁　向門口定向牆踎？","createTime":"2018-01-14T05:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T05:06:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29c0cf313ddc8178d592d8cd29a57c988a247e10","tid":528639,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20273880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273880&d=29r2hRuK8n6t4NwmtKp%2FnKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=fecfaef2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273880&h=7fad4cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20273880</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n和式踎廁　向門口定向牆踎？<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本是不少香港人的「家鄉」，久不久就會去一次，但對於日式的踎廁大家又知多少呢？最近有日本網民圖文並茂，以三大理由指出使用和式踎廁時，背對着半圓桶的罩型設計、面向門口才是正確方向，理由一：圓桶可以讓女生套上裙子（真的有人會這樣放嗎？）；二：排泄物可更快到達廁中；三：平日用洋式廁所都是面對着門口。不少網民看過後都認為很有道理，更驚呼一直以來都蹲錯了，但事實到底哪一邊才是正確方向呢？<br />\n<br />\n全新旅遊專頁，即like籽想旅行： <a href=\"https://fb.com/travel.appleseed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Ftravel.appleseed&d=29r2hRuK8n6t4NwmtKp%2FnKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=70bf3835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/travel.appleseed</a>"}]}